0.0.2.name: wordpress/like-gate
0.0.2.description:
Support

  • Support is handled on our site: http://club.orbisius.com/support/
  • Please do NOT use the WordPress forums or other places to seek support.

For a premium version of the plugin please visit http://club.orbisius.com/products/

Like Gate allows you to reveal some hidden/secret content when the user likes the article. All you have to do is insert some content between tags and that information will be shown after the like. This could be image, download link to an ebook, YouTube video (using iframe)

Benefits / Features

  • When somebody likes your article this will appear on their Facebook wall for all of their friends to see.
  • Easy to use

Demo
